    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Safexpress - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Join the Safexpress family as a Supply Chain Manager in Allahabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Safexpress:\nSafexpress is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Safexpress!",
